data.description: Looking for a gated community in West Knoxville? Look no further, this beautiful 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath home is situated on a level .25-acre lot. As you walk into the home you enter the 2-story foyer, greeted by the spacious dining room with gleaming hardwoods. As you make your way through the home you will find a main level owners suite with large on-suite & walk in closet with custom shelving. Just past the staircase you will find a 2-story great room with custom built-ins, gas fireplace flanked by two windows that allow for an abundance of natural light. Just off the great room you have an extremely well laid out kitchen with an island from prep and barstools, oversized pantry, lots of counter space with granite counter tops and a large single basin stainless sink all overlooking the eat-in breakfast area with views of the back yard. Outside you will find an extensive deck and play area making this back yard the spot for all to visit. Upstairs you have the catwalk that leads to 3 additional bedrooms, full bath, and over-sized bonus room with an abundance of storage. This home is a must see to appreciate all it has to offer. It is conveniently located to shopping, dining, interstate, Choto Market, mins to Turkey Creek for all types of entertaining. Schedule your private showing today.
